data.description: This gorgeous brick home sits on .41 acres in a large culdesac & backs into a protected area giving you privacy & peace of mind.  Sit out back in your screened in patio or enjoy an afternoon on your oversized back deck!  The home features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a bonus room that can be used as a sitting area/media room or office.  You'll love the split floor-plan & spacious vibe with tons of natural light throughout! The entire home has been freshly painted & new bathroom fixtures have been installed.  New gas water heater is in the process of being installed as well & home has a termite bond in place.  The septic tank was replaced in 2018 & HVAC in 2020.  GREAT Subdivision/Location with minimal HOA fees. Come check this property out TODAY!
